    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to get to work? This car is in fair condition and offers a great balance of functionality and value! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a reliable choice for your daily commute or weekend errands. It's a straightforward, hardworking ride that's ready for its next owner!",
