    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. Mechanically, the engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a dependable driving experience. While there may be some minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. This is a solid, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road.",
