      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. While it does start, the engine runs roughly and there is a noticeable leak in the cooling system that needs immediate repair. The exterior shows substantial wear, including visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and has a few tears. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for someone looking for a source of parts. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
